===================
Gnome image viewer
===================

Introduction
=============


Requirements
=============

To develop Gnome application you have to install these Linux packages:

    * build-essential
    * libgtk-3-dev

And for a new Gnome developer there is an API Tool un Linux called **DevHelp** which is very useful.

Description
============

Basic Gnome image viewer with ScrollBar and button to load another image.

Compile
========

GCC command to compile c application:

    * gcc -g -Wall `pkg-config --cflags gtk+-3.0` gnome-viewer.c -o gnome-viewer `pkg-config --libs gtk+-3.0`

Launch
=======

Launch using ``./gnome-viewer`` in bash.

